<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="143" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,489,884,946]" box="[151,235,920,946]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
(
<figureCitation box="[160,224,920,946]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1444,992,1739]" box="[151,868,992,1019]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,315,992,1018]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Measurement</emphasis>
. Length (including tegmen): (
<typeStatus box="[652,756,992,1019]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">holotype</typeStatus>
), 7.0 mm.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1444,992,1739]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,337,1027,1054]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Description</emphasis>
. Body pattern yellowish brown. Head with eyes faint brown (
<figureCitation box="[1023,1103,1028,1054]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1c</figureCitation>
); ocelli separated by about 
<date box="[1408,1436,1028,1054]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">4x</date>
distance from ocelli to adjacent eyes (
<figureCitation box="[570,649,1064,1090]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1a</figureCitation>
); antenna situated near upper corner of eye; anteclypeus flat and broad at base (
<figureCitation box="[245,325,1100,1126]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1c</figureCitation>
). Pronotum shorter than crown, with pair of black spots submarginally and straight lateral carinae. Scutellum yellowish with pair of semicircular brown markings; suture distinct and arched forward. Forewings opaque, veins yellow and anterior margin yellowish (
<figureCitation box="[747,827,1172,1198]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1a</figureCitation>
). Hind femur with apical setae 2+2+1.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1444,992,1739]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,371,1207,1234]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Male genitalia</emphasis>
. Pygofer side rounded with numerous setae, with notch in middle of ventral margin (
<figureCitation box="[1339,1421,1208,1235]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1d</figureCitation>
). Valve nearly pentagonal. Subgenital plate broad at base, narrowing at middle, without macrosetae, only with few marginal fine setae (
<figureCitation box="[385,467,1280,1306]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1e</figureCitation>
). Connective short and H-shaped (
<figureCitation box="[867,946,1280,1307]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1f</figureCitation>
), slightly curved in profile (
<figureCitation box="[1271,1355,1280,1306]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[1325,1355,1280,1306]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="1.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="143" unit="g" value="1.0">1g</quantity>
</figureCitation>
). Style slender, broad at base, curved laterally and acute to apex (
<figureCitation box="[835,921,1316,1343]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">Fig. 1h</figureCitation>
). Aedeagal shaft tubulose, short moderately, curved dorsad with single elongate ventral processes in lateral view, forked and expanded in middle, extending to approximately 
<date box="[320,348,1388,1414]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">2x</date>
length of aedeagal shaft in dorsal view (
<figureCitation box="[803,877,1388,1415]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1926,1951]" captionTargetBox="[208,1360,172,1898]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[207,1380,166,1907]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Bhatia longiradiata sp. nov.. a–c. Male holotype. a. Dorsal view. b. Lateral view. c. Face. d–j. Male genitalia. d. Pygofer, lateral view. e. Valve and subgenital plate, ventral view. f. Connective, ventral view. g. Connective, lateral view. h. Style, ventral view. i. Aedeagus, dorsal view. j. Aedeagus, ventral view. Scale. a–b. 1.0mm. c. 0.5mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3258448/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">
Fig. 
<date box="[855,877,1388,1415]" pageId="1" pageNumber="143">1i</date>
</figureCitation>
). Gonopore apical.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
